I just got into DC.
We have to meet.

750
00:44:03.186 --> 00:44:04.753
I figured it all out.

751
00:44:04.755 --> 00:44:07.021
Meet me at 10:00 at the place
across the square

752
00:44:07.023 --> 00:44:08.222
